Welcome to FISHEyE
Fisheries Economic Explorer


Exploring West Coast Groundfish Trawl Catch Share program data

FISHEyE is a suite of apps that are used to explore and access West Coast Groundfish Trawl Catch Share program data. The data were collected by the Northwest Fisheries Science Center (NWFSC) Economics and Social Science Program and include data from the Economic Data Collection Program, the NWFSC Pacific Coast Groundfish Social Science Survey. PacFIN data are also incorporated into the data tools.
